net/mlx5: Deprecate usage of generic TLS HW capability bit

Deprecate the generic TLS cap bit, use the new TX-specific
TLS cap bit instead.

Fixes: a12ff35e0fb7 ("net/mlx5: Introduce TLS TX offload hardware bits and structures")
